HEADWORD: Saccharine
<hw>Sac"cha*rine</hw> <pr>(? ⟦or⟧ ?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>saccharin</ets>, fr. L. <ets>saccharon</ets> sugar, Gr. <?/, <?/,
